cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.AI, cs.GR 

The paper deals with the problem of aerial image scene classification using deep convolutional neural networks (CNNs), which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The authors also mention the use of geographical data for semi-automatic annotation, which falls under information retrieval (cs.IR) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the dataset is related to geographic information systems (GIS) and remote sensing (cs.GR).
